text: Letícia Belorio (born 22 January 2001) is a Brazilian water polo player. She was part of the Brazilian women's water polo team at the 2017 World Aquatics Championships and 2019 Pan American Games. == References == == Other websites == * leticia-belorio-from-brazil- * brazils-mirella-coutinho-and-teammate- leticia-belorio Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian water polo players
